title: Wordzable v0.99.28 for Windows [FULL]
description:
OS: Windows 7, Windows 8, Windows Vista


By: LastEnd Entertainment


Language: English


Description:

Mix and twist jumbled letters to make words. Look for patterns and put your vocabulary to the test in 48 stages containing over 450 level that change each time you play. If you can find all the words in a stage that stage will unlock and allow you to return the next time you play the game.
